+/* -*- mode: C++ -*-
+ *
+ *  Copyright (C) 2007 Austin Robot Technology, Yaxin Liu, Patrick Beeson
+ *  Copyright (C) 2009 Austin Robot Technology, Jack O'Quin
+ *
+ *  License: Modified BSD Software License Agreement
+ *
